  "detailed_description": "Survival of Exon is a 2D-pixel art video game that throws you into a thrilling fight for survival.  You'll need to eliminate enemies to collect in-game currency and upgrade your character with power-ups, becoming progressively stronger and faster to overcome the increasing challenges. As the game progresses, the difficulty ramps up, demanding strategic upgrades to your gear if you want to survive the onslaught.<br><br><strong>Play On Different Maps</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855090/extras/1e318dd571377ca8b85df1652a82f03d.poster.avif?t=1717697821\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855090/extras/1e318dd571377ca8b85df1652a82f03d.webm?t=1717697821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855090/extras/1e318dd571377ca8b85df1652a82f03d.mp4?t=1717697821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Tons Of Upgrades!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855090/extras/ebd403e20e57dbac04de7cf639432b62.poster.avif?t=1717697821\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855090/extras/ebd403e20e57dbac04de7cf639432b62.webm?t=1717697821\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855090/extras/ebd403e20e57dbac04de7cf639432b62.mp4?t=1717697821\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855090/extras/5e406b42a9f9ef728e85492558a6cc39.poster.avif?t